quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Yamiroore Alla nden …ìadike, wata on hawjan nde. Senayee woodanii Mo! O toowii e ko …ìe sirkata"
  16,2,"Himo jippinira Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen e wayhu on e yamiroore Makko, dow mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, wonnde : \"Jertinree wiide rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Min. Hulee Lam"
  16,3,O tagiri kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin goonga. O toowii e ko …ìe sirkoobe sirkata ko
  16,4,O tagiri ne…ó…óanke iwde e to…ì…ìere (maniiyu); jaka yoo kanko ko wennjoowo …ìanngu…óo
  16,5,"Neemoraa…ói …óin, O tagani on …ói; no e majji nguli nugguki e nafaaji. Ko e majji kadi √±aamoton"
  16,6,"Hino woodani on e majji cu…óaari, tuma njofnoton …ói e tuma oornoton …ói"
  16,7,"Hi…ói ronndoo donle mon na…ìa e leydi ndi on yotto- tanooko si wanaa e tampere pittaali. Pellet, Joomi mon ko O Yurmetee…óo Hinnotoo…óo"
  16,8,"E pucci, e mbam-pucci, e mbabbi, fii yo on wa…ó…óo …ói, e cu…óaari. Himo taga kadi ko on anndaa"
  16,9,"Ko Alla woodani …ìanngingol laawol focciingol ngol, no e majji ngol feewaani. Si O muuyuno, O fewnay on denndaangal"
  16,10,"Ko Kanko woni jippinir…óo ndiyam ka kammu, hino woodani on e majjam njaram, le…ó…óe no (yalta) e majjam, ko e majjam kadi oornoton"
  16,11,"Himo fu…ónirana on …óam aawruuji, nebbanteeje, e tamarooje, e inabuuje, e kala dim…óe. Wonii e …óum, tasakuyee wonannde yim…ìe miijitotoo…ìe"
  16,12,"O eltani on jemma on e √±aloma on; naange ngen e lewru ndun. Koode …óen kadi ko eltiraa…óe yamiroore Makko. Wonii e …óum, tasakuyeeji wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe"
  16,13,"E ko O tagani on kon ka leydi sertu…óum nooneeji. Wonii e …óum, tasakuyee wonannde yim…ìe waajitoray…ìe"
  16,14,"Ko Kanko woni eltan…óo on maayo ngon fii yo on √±aamu e maggo teewu keccu, yaltinon e maggo cu…óaari ndi …ìornoto…óon. A yi'ay laa…óe no fe∆¥∆¥a e maggo, e fii yo on …óa…ì…ìu e …ìural Makko ngal, belajo'o, on yettay [Mo]"
  16,15,"O tuti penle ka leydi fii wata …óe dillidu e mo'on, e can…ói, e …óate, belajo'o on feeway"
  16,16,"e maandeeji [laawi]. Koode …óen hi…ìe …óowora …óe"
  16,17,E hara tagoowo on wa'ay wa on tagataa? E on waajitotaako
  16,18,"Si on lintii neemaaji Alla …óin, on moftataa …ói. Pellet, Alla ko Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  16,19,Alla no anndi ko suu…óoton e ko fe√±√±inton
  16,20,"∆äin …ói …ìe rewata gaanin Alla, …ói tagataa hay huunde, kannji tigi ko …ói tagetee…ói"
  16,21,"Ko…ói maayu…ói …ói wuuraa, …ìe so'aa-anndude nde …ìe immintintee"
  16,22,"Rewetee…óo mon on ko Rewetee…óo gooto. ∆Åen …ìe gom…óinaa laakara, …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen ko yeddu…óe, …ìen ko townitii…ìe"
  16,23,Sikke alaa wonnde Alla no anndi ko …ìe suu…óata e ko …ìe fe√±√±inta. Kanko O yi…óaa townitii…ìe …ìen
  16,24,"Si …ìe wi'anaama : \"Ko hon…óum Joomi mon jippini?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"Ko tinndi adinoo…ìe"
  16,25,"Fii yo …ìe ronndo bakkaatuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin fow √ëalnde Darngal, e bakkaatuuji …ìen …ìe majjinirta ko aldaa e ganndal; anndee bonii ko …ìe ronndoytoo"
  16,26,"Gom…óii …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe fewjiino, Alla yirbiniri mahdeele ma…ì…ìe …óen ka doose. Kippoodi ndin yanti e ma…ì…ìe, lepte …óen ardirani …ìe nokku ka …ìe so'aa-aanndude"
  16,27,"Refti √ëalnde Darngal, O hoynoyay…ìe, O wi'ana…ìe: Ko honto kafidaa…ói am …óin …ói ha…ìirayno…óon fii mun?\" ∆Åen okkaa…ìe ganndal wi'a: \"Koyeera on hannde e bone on wonii e heefer…ìe …ìen"
  16,28,"∆Åen …ìen Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen hunnata, too√±u…ìe ko'e-mun, …ìe werloo jebbilraare, (…ìe wi'a): \"Men wonaa- no gollatnoo…ìe ko boni!\" -\"Wonaa non woniri, pellet Alla ko anndu…óo ko huuwayno…óon"
  16,29,Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen luttugol ton. Nge bonii √±aa∆¥orde wonande townitii…ìe …ìen